            "en": "Place the 'tsuma' (garnish) on the plate."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "alt": {
            "ja": "ツマを敷いた皿",
            "ne": "सुमा राखेको प्लेट",
            "en": "Plate with tsuma garnish"
          },
          "path": "/images/sashimi_step1_tsuma.jpg"
        },
        {
          "type": "step",
          "text": {
            "ja": "刺身を適切な厚さに切る。",
            "ne": "साशिमीलाई उपयुक्त मोटाइमा काट्नुहोस्।",
            "en": "Slice the sashimi to the appropriate thickness."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "step",
          "text": {
            "ja": "彩りよく配置する。",
            "ne": "रंगीन ढंगले सजाउनुहोस्।",
            "en": "Arrange colorfully."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "step",
          "text": {
            "ja": "ワサビと醤油を添える。",
            "ne": "वासाबी र सोयु सससँगै राख्नुहोस्।",
            "en": "Serve with wasabi and soy sauce."
          }
        }
      ],
      "image": "/images/sashimi.jpg"
    }
  ]
}
